Capturing My Fitness Journey 🎥

latestPosts.caption:
After 3 years of back to back defeats, I finally made it, secured 3rd place in the 60kg category at the 25th Arm Wrestling State Level Championship, Arunachal Pradesh.
All thanks to my second home, 8letic Gym, which gave me everything I needed strength, support, and a place to grow.
To my friends and family who stood by me through every fall, this win is for us. Next time gold for sure 💪🏻

#armwrestling #gyminspiration #fitnmotivation
